00:12:47.576 --> 00:12:50.076 A:middle
and disconnect controllers
in your game and you're going

00:12:50.076 --> 00:12:51.506 A:middle
to want to handle
those appropriately.

00:12:53.136 --> 00:12:56.776 A:middle
I'm also going to talk about
how to read controller inputs.

00:12:57.006 --> 00:13:00.376 A:middle
So, once your game knows which
controller or controllers it has

WEBVTT
X-TIMESTAMP-MAP=MPEGTS:181083,LOCAL:00:00:00.000

00:13:00.566 --> 00:13:03.486 A:middle
to access how do you actually
read what the thumbsitck

00:13:03.486 --> 00:13:04.056 A:middle
position is?

00:13:04.056 --> 00:13:05.856 A:middle
How do you read what
player is pushing

00:13:05.856 --> 00:13:08.726 A:middle
as far as face buttons goes?

