00:13:26.586 --> 00:13:29.526 A:middle
How to take all this
technical information and think

00:13:29.526 --> 00:13:32.166 A:middle
about all this new
capabilities afforded to you

00:13:32.376 --> 00:13:35.066 A:middle
so that you can integrate
game controllers in a away

00:13:35.066 --> 00:13:36.416 A:middle
that makes your games
really special.

