notice I can detect the four

00:36:22.716 --> 00:36:25.146 A:middle
cardinal and the four
inter cardinal directions.

00:36:25.146 --> 00:36:27.746 A:middle
I can also just take
the pressure right now.

00:36:27.746 --> 00:36:29.866 A:middle
So, you I' pushing the
left as hard as I can.

00:36:29.866 --> 00:36:31.686 A:middle
I can also push it less hard.

00:36:32.416 --> 00:36:35.886 A:middle
So, you there's a float
value between zero and one

00:36:36.006 --> 00:36:37.136 A:middle
for the direction I'm pushing.

00:36:37.826 --> 00:36:41.026 A:middle
This actually allows
you to get 360 degrees

00:36:41.416 --> 00:36:42.846 A:middle
of analog input on the D-pad.

00:36:44.106 --> 00:36:45.536 A:middle
The same applies to face buttons

00:36:45.706 --> 00:36:48.926 A:middle
so as I press A you
notice first it's pressed

00:36:48.926 --> 00:36:51.986 A:middle
and I can press it harder
enlarging the circle there is,

00:36:52.756 --> 00:36:55.426 A:middle
B the same, X and Y

00:36:56.386 --> 00:37:00.116 A:middle
and of course the shoulder
buttons too, right and left.

WEBVTT
